description: The investment seeks to track the investment results (before fees and expenses) of the Invesco Revenue Weighted International Index (the "underlying index"). The fund generally will invest at least 90% of its total assets in the securities that comprise the underlying index, as well as ADRs and GDRs that represent securities in the underlying index. The underlying index consists of all of the constituent securities of the MSCI EAFE Index. The fund is non-diversified.
name: Invesco International Revenue ETF
